  <name>Roll-It</name>
  <summary>Roll the dice</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Roll a six-sided die by default, or roll a custom die of up to one-hundred sides.</p>

    <p>Copy roll results to the clipboard from the history pane. Results are remembered until the app is closed or they are manually cleared.</p>

    <p>Keyboard shortcuts:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Roll the dice with Ctrl+R</li>
      <li>Copy the last result with Ctrl+C</li>
      <li>Toggle the roll history pane with Ctrl+H</li>
      <li>Clear roll history with Ctrl+L</li>
      <li>Undo the clear with Ctrl+Z</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
